import Description from "./Description"
import React from "react"
import { Container,Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"

const MenuOption = () => {

    return(
        <React.Fragment>
            <Container>
            <Description></Description>
                <Row>
                <input></input>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        
            <button>+Add</button>
        </React.Fragment>
    )

}

export default MenuOption
